{"tid":1883330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角超市遭3人持刀打劫 搶走價值千多元廁紙","createTime":"2020-02-17T01:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T14:45:22.000Z","uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b9c5c2d89556864d802f3165e608c1c9477215a","tid":1883330,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:03:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">旺角超市遭3人持刀打劫 搶走價值千多元廁紙</span></strong></span><br />\n旺角一間超市外，有3名男子持刀搶走價值千幾元的廁紙。<br />\n<br />\n警方在6時許接報，指一名送貨工人在旺角道97號，被3名男子持刀威嚇，搶走一批在超市外的廁紙，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IN4NS1f620_cnlquqh73cw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/726598e0-5117-11ea-bb7f-ef4ed5be6d66\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIN4NS1f620_cnlquqh73cw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F726598e0-5117-11ea-bb7f-ef4ed5be6d66&h=cff76ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n😂😂👍🧻<br />\n延伸閱讀<br />\n屌那星 鼻敏感全屋得返兩卷廁紙。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1882988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1882988</a>"},{"pid":"dd60b1504bab5a5f47b7e6165f6a2b0bf8fd5a87","tid":1883330,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"痾屎冇廁紙都咪話唔大鑊"},{"pid":"e67dd0e510f4188a8198df7455216e88517092cb","tid":1883330,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"邊個做㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e99b9f0d7b2439b3e5018ea8d6184b2ddf82c4","tid":1883330,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,